name: MSRI-SIX-GIFBYG-01
description: v4w.enko - "MSRI-SIX-GIFBYG-01" Is a six projection artwork. There are 6 gif animations of a one 3d Object which is  generated with custom definition. 2 lofts are animated in 2 layers for each color: Yellow  and  Blue. The cells of the Green "3d voronoi" cube are linked to the attractor`s points which are extracted from the 2 lofts. The 6 views are forming the 6-projections canvas of the different views of the same object in the same scale 512*512 pixels each screen. Order of projection is from upper left to down right is: Left, Front, Top, Bottom, Back, Right.  Total 64 frames, 1024*1536 px canvas.
